snippet.title: Argus | Hero Overview | Predecessor
snippet.description:
Argus, Mad Mage of the Soul Storm is Predecessor's latest original Hero! In this video, we'll be going over Argus' impressive kit to help you dominate the Midlane when he launches on March 5th.

Check out all Argus has to offer on our website: https://predecessorgame.com/heroes/Argus
